required

pattern="regular expression"
title="message"
regex (regular expression)
------

[a-z A-Z]   will allow only one character
[a-z A-Z]+   multiple characters
[a-z A-Z] {30}  allow fixed 30 characters
[a-z A-Z] {3,30}  allow min 3 and max 30 characters
[a-z A-Z] {3,}  allow min 3 and max unlimited characters
[a-z A-Z] {,40} 
[0-9] 
[0-9]+
[0-9] {10}



