===============

operators
Arithmetic
+,-,*,%

Logical
&& || !

Relational
>,<,>=,==,!=,<=,==,===

var a=20
var b="20"
k=(a==b) true
k=(a===b) false will chk type and value both

Assignment Operator
+=,-=,*=,/=,%=,=
var k=10
k+=100  110
k+=2    112

Unary Operator
++, --

Ternary Operator
?
<condition>?<true>:<false>
var a=100
var b=20
k=a>b?"<h1>Hello</h1>":"<h1>Hi</hi>"


